  "body_html": "<!DOCTYPE html\n  SYSTEM \"about:legacy-compat\">\n<html lang=\"en-us\" dir=\"ltr\"><head><title>Class Position</title><meta charset=\"utf-8\"><link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" media=\"screen,projection\" href=\"/resource/css/style-v2.css\"><script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"js/sap-strings.js\"></script></head><body class=\"en-us sap-light centered navigation-default enumeration-disabled\"><div id=\"d4h5-main-container\" class=\"container_12\" role=\"application\"><div id=\"d4h5-section-container\" class=\"grid_12\"><div id=\"d4h5-main-content\" class=\"grid_8 alpha omega\"><section><div class=\"page topic  - topic-topic \" id=\"loioc61ada531198434de10000000a174cb4\"><h1 class=\"title topictitle1\">Class Position</h1><div class=\"body\">\n<p class=\"p\"><span class=\"ph emphasis emphasis\">Use</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\"> The class position list shows for each company code and ID number, on a specific date, the positions of a class in the various securities accounts.\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\">The list is displayed via the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">SAP List Viewer</span> .\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\">You can display the following columns:\n</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\"><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">Securities account\n</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">Securities account name\n</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">Nominal\n</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">Nominal currency\n</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">Units\n</p></li></ul>\n</div></div></section><div class=\"clear\"></div>\n</div></div></div></body></html>"
